"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388832","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","false","2015-07-16","<p>The British Government has not made representations to the Government of Germany on this matter.</p>",,"Baroness Anelay of St Johns",,"2015-07-16T15:05:35.493Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388832/answer","Biography information for Baroness Anelay of St Johns","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388832/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388832/answer",,,,,"16","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","2015-07-09","Namibia: Germany","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty’s Government what representations they have made to the government of Germany regarding compensation for the descendants of the Herero and Nama people killed by German colonial troops in German South-West Africa in 1904–08.","false","Biography information for Lord Steel of Aikwood",,"Lord Steel of Aikwood","HL1309"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388834","Attorney General","false","2015-07-14","<p>I refer the Hon. Member to the answer my Right Hon. Friend the Minister for the Cabinet Office gave on 13<sup>th</sup> July 2015 to Question <a href="http://www.parliament.uk/business/publications/written-questions-answers-statements/written-question/Commons/2015-07-07/5983/" target="_blank">5983</a>.</p>","Kenilworth and Southam","Jeremy Wright",,"2015-07-14T16:16:25.053Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388834/answer","Biography information for Jeremy Wright","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388834/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388834/answer",,,,,"88","Attorney General","Attorney General","2015-07-09","Attorney General: Ministerial Policy Advisers","1","House of Commons","To ask the Attorney General, what the name, responsibilities and pay band are of each special adviser in the Law Officers' Departments.","false","Biography information for Stuart Blair Donaldson","West Aberdeenshire and Kincardine","Stuart Blair Donaldson","6321"
