"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388851","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills","false","2015-07-15","<p>The Government is committed to the Catapult programme.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p>My Rt hon Friend the Chancellor of the Exchequer announced during his visit to Alderley Park on 13 July a new Medicines Technologies Catapult to build on the UK’s excellence in life sciences.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p>We will continue to work with Innovate UK, businesses, universities and others to identify further opportunities.</p><p> </p>","Orpington","Joseph Johnson",,"2015-07-15T15:29:11.173Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388851/answer","Biography information for Joseph  Johnson","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388851/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388851/answer",,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2015-07-09","Technology and Innovation Centres","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, what plans he has for opening new Catapult centres.","false","Biography information for Chuka Umunna","Streatham","Mr Chuka Umunna","6485"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388852","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills","false","2015-07-16","<p>The internal review of employment status has now concluded and Ministers are considering the findings.</p>","Grantham and Stamford","Nick Boles",,"2015-07-16T14:44:38.793Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388852/answer","Biography information for Nick Boles","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388852/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388852/answer",,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2015-07-09","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills: Staff","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, what progress his Department has made on its consultation on clarifying the employment status of workers, launched on 6 October 2014.","false","Biography information for Chuka Umunna","Streatham","Mr Chuka Umunna","6424"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388853","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills","false","2015-07-15","<p>The Next Generation Digital Economy Centres, announced in the Summer Budget, will start work on or by 1 October 2015 with the exception of the Centre in Swansea which is already operational.</p><p> </p>","Orpington","Joseph Johnson",,"2015-07-15T15:30:44.173Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388853/answer","Biography information for Joseph  Johnson","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388853/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388853/answer",,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2015-07-09","Digital Technology","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, by what date he plans for each of the six next generation digital economy centres to be operational.","false","Biography information for Chuka Umunna","Streatham","Mr Chuka Umunna","6486"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388854","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills","false","2015-07-17","<p>As outlined in the March 2015 Budget, £138 million of public funding has been allocated to the UK Collaboratorium for Research in Infrastructure and Cities (UKCRIC) – subject to business case approval. The funding for UKCRIC, as well as the operational date of the Co-ordination Node (hub), is to be determined as part of the business case.</p>","Orpington","Joseph Johnson",,"2015-07-17T10:41:30.487Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388854/answer","Biography information for Joseph  Johnson","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388854/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388854/answer",,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2015-07-09","Infrastructure: Research","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, by what date he plans for the Collaboration for Research in Infrastructure and Cities hub to be operational; and what funds have been provided from the public purse to establish that hub.","false","Biography information for Chuka Umunna","Streatham","Mr Chuka Umunna","6425"
